  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BULLET HELL + MUSIC + ROGUELITE = BEAT BLAST </h2> The music you make becomes your abilities <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072640/extras/78d11cb18444a26a5297d9546fc17770.poster.avif?t=1638977212\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072640/extras/78d11cb18444a26a5297d9546fc17770.webm?t=1638977212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072640/extras/78d11cb18444a26a5297d9546fc17770.mp4?t=1638977212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Musical Journey</h2><br>Fight against big bosses, unlock tons of items and try to escape the MIDIverse, a virus-ridden technical realm where music takes physical form.<br><br>The MIDIverse is full of abilities that can be combined to support hundreds of different styles of play. At the heart of it all is your song; a looping beat that can be tweaked at any time to completely change the rhythm of the gameplay.<br><br>No two runs are the same and each run has its own soundtrack...one that you create.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072640/extras/647615cef5c29173761c296dceff7650.poster.avif?t=1638977212\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072640/extras/647615cef5c29173761c296dceff7650.webm?t=1638977212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072640/extras/647615cef5c29173761c296dceff7650.mp4?t=1638977212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072640/extras/c32675a412050fce0a47485c64fddb4d.poster.avif?t=1638977212\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072640/extras/c32675a412050fce0a47485c64fddb4d.webm?t=1638977212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072640/extras/c32675a412050fce0a47485c64fddb4d.mp4?t=1638977212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >...Full of Challenges</h2><br>If the MIDIverse doesn’t present enough of a challenge, you can test your skills against other players in weekly high score and speedrun competitions.<br><br>Groove to your own beats and see how far you can go. Can you create a song that can best the worst the MIDIverse has to offer? Can you help spot on his journey home?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1072640/extras/e35fa25291567a96b554609ea4a02353.avif?t=1638977212\" width=620 height=470 /></span>",
